<p>
  <span class="nym">Amadeus</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym">'loved by God', from <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>amo</i> 'I love' + <i>deus</i> 'God'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 12th C French saint.</p>
</div>
  
  


